  "text": "In the sensitivity analysis, we further examined the contribution from the length of campaign impact by assuming the campaign effect would continue for 8 years and would increase the total aspirin use population from 36% to 81%. We assumed the adherence to aspirin is 100% [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] and varied it (50%-100%) in the sensitivity analysis.",
